176
00:12:33,957 --> 00:12:36,024
What, Ken? No, no.
Ken's a puppy dog.

177
00:12:36,024 --> 00:12:38,105
Hey Lance,
tell the man you raced against Ken.

178
00:12:38,105 --> 00:12:41,087
However, I've driven more
behind him than against him.

179
00:12:41,447 --> 00:12:45,891
