01:30:32,677 --> 01:30:35,586
even the RPMs are determined by us.

1225
01:30:39,182 --> 01:30:41,917
<i>Ken Miles is locked in a
pitched battle with Hansgen</i>

1226
01:30:41,918 --> 01:30:43,729
<i>as they pass the grandstand.</i>

1227
01:30:47,231 --> 01:30:50,612
<i>Hansgen is taking a run at
Miles into turn one.</i>

1228
01:30:53,209 --> 01:30:54,607
<i>Hansgen takes the lead...</i>

1229
01:31:05,768 --> 01:31:08,262
Oh, blimey! Did you see that?

1230
01:31:16,367 --> 01:31:17,609
Still racing.

