1255
01:32:39,406 --> 01:32:41,227
Go to bed, it's 1 AM.

1256
01:32:41,227 --> 01:32:43,189
- Ask him.
- Go to bed! Now!

1257
01:32:43,768 --> 01:32:45,307
I take it he's not asleep.

1258
01:32:45,308 --> 01:32:47,282
<i>I'm sure he smuggled in a radio.</i>

1259
01:32:48,604 --> 01:32:50,014
He said to ask how are the brakes.

1260
01:32:50,015 --> 01:32:54,156
The brakes, yes.
No, no, tell him they're working, for now.

1261
01:32:54,393 --> 01:32:56,630
You know,
Shelby's been acting very strange.

1262
01:32:57,389 --> 01:32:58,518
<i>- Ford's gonna...</i>
- Ken.

1263
01:32:58,518 --> 01:33:00,705
<i>push up another team with a GT.</i>

